43:45.208 --> 43:47.667
- and disappeared.
- Okay.

43:47.667 --> 43:49.917
In three days,
you're gonna hire a PI.

43:49.917 --> 43:51.667
I'm gonna give you a name.

43:51.667 --> 43:53.458
The guy's a fucking idiot,
but eventually

43:53.458 --> 43:54.792
he's gonna figure out
that Varick took the money

43:54.792 --> 43:56.208
and fled to Belize.

43:56.208 --> 43:57.792
Let him leak the story.

43:57.792 --> 43:59.083
The papers will run something
about the divorce.

43:59.083 --> 44:00.375
They'll come to you
for a comment.

44:00.375 --> 44:02.125
Don't give 'em one.

44:02.125 --> 44:02.959
You got it?

44:02.959 --> 44:04.417
I got it.

44:06.417 --> 44:10.542
Paige, dear,
thank you for coming over.

44:10.542 --> 44:13.500
Varick stole $8 million
from the fund

44:13.500 --> 44:16.667
- I set up for you and him.
- How?

44:16.667 --> 44:18.375
We don't know,
but the money's gone.

44:18.375 --> 44:21.834
He's gone,
and we're sure he did it.

44:21.834 --> 44:24.375
And I've also been thinking
about the Napier deal,

44:24.375 --> 44:25.709
and I've reconsidered
my position.

44:25.709 --> 44:27.417
I'm gonna pay Napier's ask.

44:27.417 --> 44:29.709
We'll acquire the rest
of the land,

44:29.709 --> 44:33.500
and then I'm gonna let you
run the show.

44:34.750 --> 44:36.291
Why?

44:36.291 --> 44:39.542
'Cause it's a good idea,

44:39.542 --> 44:43.166
and because it's time for me
to step aside and let you lead.

44:47.333 --> 44:49.291
Well, it has to be done
by tonight.

44:49.291 --> 44:50.333
Just call Napier.

44:50.333 --> 44:51.959
Close the deal, hmm?

44:51.959 --> 44:55.542
I need a couple of more minutes
with Ray, anyway.

44:58.333 --> 45:00.542
Thank you for this.

45:07.625 --> 45:10.542
Where'd you bury him?

45:10.542 --> 45:13.166
- I can't tell you that.
- Where'd you bury him?

45:13.166 --> 45:16.000
I can't tell you. Trust me,
it's better if you don't know.

45:19.375 --> 45:21.959
Will you sit with me
for a moment, hmm?

45:21.959 --> 45:25.000
- That's all he's gonna get.
- What do you mean?

45:25.000 --> 45:29.750
His funeral will be
you and me sitting together.

45:31.959 --> 45:33.834
Right.

45:50.500 --> 45:52.333
Thank you, Ray.

46:06.000 --> 46:08.000
[exhales deeply]

46:08.000 --> 46:09.709
So how'd you get my father
to change his mind?

46:09.709 --> 46:11.709
I'm helping him deal
with Varick.

46:11.709 --> 46:12.875
Varick stealing
my trust fund

46:12.875 --> 46:14.834
