to my father.

46:14.834 --> 46:16.458
Maybe you do.

46:16.458 --> 46:18.959
"The passport
is the fix"?

46:21.542 --> 46:22.917
You made a side deal.
I know you.

46:22.917 --> 46:25.625
You got what you wanted,
didn't you?

46:31.834 --> 46:33.208
Fine.

46:35.750 --> 46:37.917
Congratulations, partner.

46:41.834 --> 46:44.625
Congratulations.

47:08.375 --> 47:11.750
[laughter]

47:11.750 --> 47:12.959
[Bunchy]
Let me remind you

47:12.959 --> 47:16.875
