of like Edith Bunker now.

47:31.041 --> 47:35.625
Archie! Archie,
come down here and walk Pluto.

47:35.625 --> 47:37.750
He keeps licking my toes.

47:37.750 --> 47:39.875
Go on,
go to the kitchen...

47:43.583 --> 47:45.166
Watch, dear Lord,

47:45.166 --> 47:49.166
